<figureCitation id="13512A00FFC4FFD2FCB8F903BC5FC80F" box="[793,874,1774,1801]" captionStart="FIGURE 16" captionStartId="24.[136,229,676,698]" captionTargetBox="[177,1411,190,652]" captionTargetId="figure-22@24.[177,1411,190,652]" captionTargetPageId="24" captionText="FIGURE 16. Puccinia urticata on Carex sp. A. Telia on the leaf surface. B. Teliospores. C. Vertical section of a telium. Scale bars: B, C = 20 μm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6416806" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6416806/files/figure.png" pageId="23" pageNumber="244">Fig. 16</figureCitation>
